---

## Key Concepts Demonstrated

- Relational schema design with primary and foreign key constraints
- Stored procedure with cursor-based iteration and transaction control
- Before-insert trigger for enforcing business rules at the database layer
- Auto-increment as an equivalent to Oracle sequences
- Full-stack integration: frontend → REST API → stored procedure → MySQL
- Random seat assignment with collision handling and retry logic
